50|$|Ursavini is an extinct {{tribe of}} mammals {{of the family}} <b>Ursidae</b> (bears) endemic to North America, Europe, Africa, and Asia during Miocene through Pliocene, living from about 23—2.5 Mya, {{existing}} for roughly 23-2.5 million years.|$|E
